119
00:18:18,712 --> 00:18:31,469
Still, when he smells that savage musk, the rending gory bison herds are as present as to the deserted wild foal of the prairies, which this instant they may be trampling into dust.

120
00:18:31,489 --> 00:18:38,458
Thus then, the muffle-rollings of a milky sea, the bleak rustlings of the festooned frosts of mountains,

121
00:18:38,438 --> 00:18:48,819
