122
00:18:49,099 --> 00:19:00,582
Though neither knows where lie the nameless things of which the mystic sign gives forth such hints, yet with me, as with the colt, somewhere those things must insist.

123
00:19:00,562 --> 00:19:08,771
Though, in many of its aspects, this visible world seems formed in love, the invisible spheres were formed in fright.

124
00:19:09,051 --> 00:19:20,744
But not yet have we solved the incantation of this whiteness, and learned why it appeals with such power to the soul, and more strange and far more portentous why, as we have seen.

125
00:19:20,764 --> 00:19:24,728
